      "system": {
        "description": { "value": "<p>If the vampire isn't in sunlight, it can use its action to polymorph into a Large hyena or a Medium cloud of mist, or back into its true form. While in hyena form, the vampire can't speak, and its walking speed is 50 feet. While in mist form, the vampire can't take any actions, speak, or manipulate objects; it is weightless, has a flying speed of 20 feet, can hover, and can enter a hostile creature's space. It has advantage on Str, Dex, and Con saving throws and is immune to all nonmagical damage except sunlight.</p>", "chat": "" },
        "type": { "value": "monster" },
